        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") The weapons of the multitude.—",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ἐκρύβη",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "He hid Himself",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") Not by betaking Himself to a hiding-place, but that He ceased to be visible to their eyes, in a miraculous manner; (comp. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
