        "text": ", “The king commanded—to take Baruch and Jeremiah; but ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "the Lord hid",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " them”) whilst He went out from the temple.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
