            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "note_emph",
        "text": "(7)",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "The conflict and the victory. Therefore",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "The conflict and the victory. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "cmt_word",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "Therefore",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " - because he said this, which if it had no basis in [act was rank blasphemy - ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "they took up stones",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " of the temple court ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "to cast at",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (upon) ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "him",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". \"They rushed from the porch into the court of the Gentiles, to pick up stones to cast them at him; but once more 'his hour had not yet come,' and their fury proved impotent. Hiding himself in one  of the many passages or gateways of the temple, he presently passed out\" (Edersheim). ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "But Jesus hid himself, and went forth from",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "the temple",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " [ going through the midst of them, and so passed by]. There is no need to imagine more than the exercise of his majestic energy before which daemoniacs quailed, and Pilate trembled, and the guards of the temple fell abashed. The crisis of his ministry in Jerusalem is approaching. How often would he have gathered them, and given to them eternal life, but ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "they",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " would not! ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
